snippet.title: Legend of Krannia - BARBARIAN GAMEPLAY
snippet.description:
Hello Krannians!

Today, we'll be Playing Legend of Krannia: Cursed Fate and we will use a Barbarian build. This video will show you the gameplay and basic management for your Barbarian Deck and Stats. Let us know what you think of the build! 

If you want to see more build, you can subscribe to our channel.
We'll be also creating a Mage build and we will be releasing a lot more Gameplay videos. If you have any comments or feedback, don't hesitate to comment bellow or join our discord channel.

Thank you and see you in the next video!

Get your Copy NOW!! Take advantage of the Early Access! 
Steam -  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1458340/Legend_of_Krannia_Cursed_Fate/
